(354, 'http://www.larmoiredelana.com/?p=10278', 'Around the World: Breakfast at Maison Dior – #PFW', 'http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2784-768x1024.jpg', 'On Tuesday March 5th, several fashion bloggers and members of the press were invited to Dior’s main store in Avenue Mo...', 'larmoiredelana', 1363389060, '<p><span>On Tuesday March 5th, several fashion bloggers and members of the press were invited to Dior’s main store in Avenue Montaigne for a re-see of the Fall Winter 2013 collection. During the re-see, we enjoyed an exquisite breakfast, while listening to several specialists explaining to us in detail different aspects of the collections and the inspiration behind them.</span><br><span>Next, there was a room with a setting close to the one during the fashion show and every blogger could chose his favorite look and recreate it on the mannequin. It was so much fun! I decided to go for a corset and dress outfit, the black talon virgule shoes and the Andy Warrhol printed Lady Dior. I fell in love with the combination of light pink, black and white and I really wanted to reproduce it.</span><br><a href="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2783.jpg" rel="lightbox[10278]"><img title="IMG_2783" src="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2783-768x1024.jpg" alt="IMG 2783 768x1024 Around the World: Breakfast at Maison Dior   #PFW" width="584" height="778"></a><a href="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2819.jpg" rel="lightbox[10278]"><img title="IMG_2819" src="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2819-1024x768.jpg" alt="IMG 2819 1024x768 Around the World: Breakfast at Maison Dior   #PFW" width="584" height="438"></a><a href="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2784.jpg" rel="lightbox[10278]"><img title="IMG_2784" src="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2784-768x1024.jpg" alt="IMG 2784 768x1024 Around the World: Breakfast at Maison Dior   #PFW" width="584" height="778"></a></p>\n<div><a href="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2834.jpg" rel="lightbox[10278]"><img title="IMG_2834" src="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2834-768x1024.jpg" alt="IMG 2834 768x1024 Around the World: Breakfast at Maison Dior   #PFW" width="584" height="778"></a><p>Reconstituted my favorite look from Dior FW13, what do you think!?</p></div>\n<p><span>Click on the pictures below to make them bigger and look through the gallery! The details are fab!</span></p>\n\n<a href="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/?attachment_id=10365" title="IMG_2774"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2774-150x150.jpg" alt="IMG 2774 150x150 Around the World: Breakfast at Maison Dior   #PFW" title="IMG_2774"></a>\n<a href="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/?attachment_id=10369" title="IMG_2782"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2782-150x150.jpg" alt="IMG 2782 150x150 Around the World: Breakfast at Maison Dior   #PFW" title="IMG_2782"></a>\n<a href="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/?attachment_id=10372" title="IMG_2783"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2783-150x150.jpg" alt="IMG 2783 150x150 Around the World: Breakfast at Maison Dior   #PFW" title="IMG_2783"></a>\n<a href="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/?attachment_id=10373" title="IMG_2784"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2784-150x150.jpg" alt="IMG 2784 150x150 Around the World: Breakfast at Maison Dior   #PFW" title="IMG_2784"></a>\n<a href="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/?attachment_id=10374" title="IMG_2786"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://www.larmoiredelana.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/IMG_2786-150x150.jpg" alt="IMG 2786 150x150 Around the World: Breakfast at 