(587, 'http://www.nogarlicnoonions.com/ngnos-cranberries-quinoa-salad/', 'NGNO’S Cranberries Quinoa Salad', NULL, 'The name Quinoa is derived from the Spanish name Kinwa. It originated in the Andean region of Ecuador, Peru, Colombia an...', 'nogarlicnoonions', 1364193840, 'The name Quinoa is derived from the Spanish name Kinwa. It originated in the Andean region of Ecuador, Peru, Colombia and Bolivia.  Quinoa is a grain-like crop grown for its edible seeds. It is not considered to be a true cereal as it is not a member of the true grass family. It is more<a href="http://www.nogarlicnoonions.com/ngnos-cranberries-quinoa-salad/">  »more...</a>'),
