(589, 'http://thejrexpress.com/2013/03/23/paypal-coming-to-lebanon-in-2013-why-we-had-to-wait-that-much/', 'PayPal Coming To Lebanon In 2013 – Why We Had To Wait That Much?', NULL, 'Elias Ghanem, MENA general manager of PayPal, announced at the ArabNet 2013 Conference in Beirut that the famous online ...', 'thejrexpress', 1364007000, 'Elias Ghanem, MENA general manager of PayPal, announced at the ArabNet 2013 Conference in Beirut that the famous online payment service will soon be available in Lebanon. And this is most probably happening this year. I had the chance to discuss with Mr. Ghanem (in company of Blog Baladi and Gino’s Blog) after his public [...]<img alt="" border="0" src="http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=thejrexpress.com&blog=15937828&post=1842&subd=expressjr&ref=&feed=1" width="1" height="1">'),
(590, 'http://blogbaladi.com/road-safety-dbayeh-highway/', 'Road Safety (Dbayeh Highway)', 'http://blogbaladi.com/images/20130323_083508-425x317.jpg', 'Just imagine what could have happened if there was a car behind that pickup when this huge board fell off. What’s even...', 'blogbaladi', 1364194380, '<p><img src="http://blogbaladi.com/images/20130323_083508-425x317.jpg" alt="20130323_083508" width="425" height="317"></p>\n<p>Just imagine what could have happened if there was a car behind that pickup when this huge board fell off. What’s even worse is that he’s driving on the fast lane instead of staying on the extreme right and going slowly. </p>\n<p><img src="http://blogbaladi.com/images/20130323_083510-425x309.jpg" alt="20130323_083510" width="425" height="309"></p>\n<p>Meanwhile …</p>\n<p><img src="http://blogbaladi.com/images/lol2-425x425.jpg" alt="" title="lol" width="425" height="425"></p>'),
