(619, 'http://blog.octavianasr.com/2013/03/egypts-future-in-little-brave-rajaas.html', 'Egypt’s future in little brave Rajaa’s hands', NULL, 'As soon as I landed in Cairo, I could feel the heaviness of life, economy, politics and breath. It didn’t take long fo...', 'octavianasr', 1364227920, 'As soon as I landed in Cairo, I could feel the heaviness of life, economy, politics and breath. It didn’t take long for the first Egyptian to blurt that things were “better under Mubarak’s dictatorship than they are in the Muslim Brotherhood’s lair.” A slew of similar observations followed, mostly from poor people like a taxi driver who told me he sometimes works all day long to barely avoid'),
(620, 'http://meandbeirut.com/2013/03/25/schnitzels/', 'Schnitzels', 'http://meandbeirut.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/img_3246.jpg?w=500&h=450', 'Somebody asked me recently why there are no German restaurants in Lebanon. Well, there is one, at City Mall. It’s call...', 'meandbeirut', 1364230740, '<p><a href="http://meandbeirut.com/2013/03/25/schnitzels/img_3246/" rel="attachment wp-att-3013"><img src="http://meandbeirut.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/img_3246.jpg?w=500&h=450" alt="mmmm :)" width="500" height="450"></a></p>\n<p>Somebody asked me recently why there are no German restaurants in Lebanon. Well, there is one, at City Mall. It’s called “Schnitzels”, like the German word for escalope. It’s an “authentic German restaurant”, they assure you, but Schnitzels are of course eaten in many other countries, especially in Österreich/Austria, but also in Iran and Israel, as I just read! The waitresses at Schnitzels wear the traditional “Dirndl” dresses, and even the hands on the picture are authentic German by the way; this is my friend’s brother who is trying the Jägerschnitzel (I think), which means Schnitzel with a champignon sauce. Ok, enough said, it’s time to eat. Yalla, essen <img src="http://s0.wp.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":-)"></p>\n<br>Filed under: <a href="http://meandbeirut.com/category/cafes-restos/">CAFÉS & RESTOS</a> Tagged: <a href="http://meandbeirut.com/tag/beirut/">Beirut</a>, <a href="http://meandbeirut.com/tag/cuisine/">Cuisine</a>, <a href="http://meandbeirut.com/tag/deutschland/">Deutschland</a>, <a href="http://meandbeirut.com/tag/food/">Food</a>, <a href="http://meandbeirut.com/tag/germany/">Germany</a>, <a href="http://meandbeirut.com/tag/lebanon/">Lebanon</a>, <a href="http://meandbeirut.com/tag/photography/">Photography</a>, <a href="http://meandbeirut.com/tag/schnitzel/">Schnitzel</a>, <a href="http://meandbeirut.com/tag/travel/">Travel</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"></a> <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"></a> <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/facebook/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"></a> <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gotwitter/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/twitter/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"></a> <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gostumble/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/stumble/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"></a> <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godigg/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/digg/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"></a> <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/goreddit/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/reddit/meandbeirut.wordpress.com/3012/"></a> <img alt="" border="0" src="http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=meandbeirut.com&blog=31277394&post=3012&subd=meandbeirut&ref=&feed=1" width="1" height="1">'),
(621, 'http://sansglutenabeyrouth.blogspot.com/2013/03/lily-bejjani-championne-et-sans-gluten.html', 'Lily Bejjani, championne et sans gluten!', NULL, 'Lily Bejjani est intolérante au gluten et une passionnée de course à pied. En l''espace de quelques mois, elle a déj...', 'sansglutenabeyrouth', 1364233800, '<div dir="ltr" trbidi="on"><div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-T1VGpbMR5As/UVBLRNJGnEI/AAAAAAAAEWk/v4a_l7iXI_4/s1600/photo+nike.JPG" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="320" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-T1VGpbMR5As/UVBLRNJGnEI/AAAAAAAAEWk/v4a_l7iXI_4/s320/photo+nike.JPG" width="239"></a></div><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml> <w:WordDocument>  <w:View>Normal</w:View>  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>  <w:TrackMoves/>  <w:TrackFormatting/>  <w:PunctuationKerning/>  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/>  <w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>  <w:LidThemeAsian>X-NONE</w:LidThemeAsian>  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>AR-SA</w:LidThemeComplexScript>  <w:Compatibility>   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>   <w:SplitPgBreakAndParaMark/>   <w:DontVertAlignCellWithSp/>   <w:DontBreakConstrainedForcedTables/>   <w:DontVertAlignInTxbx/>   <w:Word11KerningPairs/>   <w:CachedColBalance/>  </w:Compatibility>  <m:mathPr>   <m:mathFont m:val="Cambria Math"/>   <m:brkBin m:val="before"/>   <m:brkBinSub m:val="--"/>   <m:smallFrac m:val="off"/>   <m:dispDef/>   <m:lMargin m:val="0"/>   <m:rMargin m:val="0"/>   <m:defJc m:val="centerGroup"/>   <m:wrapIndent m:val="1440"/>   <m:intLim m:val="subSup"/>   <m:naryLim m:val="undOvr"/>  </m:mathPr></w:WordDocument></xml><![endif]--> <br><div><br></div><div><span><b><span><span lang="FR-CA"><span>Lily Bejjani est </span></span></span></b></span><span><b><span><span lang="FR-CA"><span><span><spa