(969, 'http://www.nogarlicnoonions.com/al-halabi-antelias-restaurant-visiting-again/', 'Al Halabi: A Revamped Look… Same Old Taste', 'http://www.nogarlicnoonions.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Al_Halabi_Antelias_Lebanese_Restaurant49-300x300.jpg', 'For the past decade or so, Al Halabi restaurant in Antelias has maintained its reputation for being one of the top ran...', 'nogarlicnoonions', 1365141600, '<img width="300" height="300" src="http://www.nogarlicnoonions.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Al_Halabi_Antelias_Lebanese_Restaurant49-300x300.jpg" alt="Al_Halabi_Antelias_Lebanese_Restaurant49">For the past decade or so, Al Halabi restaurant in Antelias has maintained its reputation for being one of the top ranking Lebanese restaurants in town. A restaurant with a history that has only  developed positively with time. The owners, a man and his wife, have continuously made sure to be present on a daily basis to<a href="http://www.nogarlicnoonions.com/al-halabi-antelias-restaurant-visiting-again/">  »more...</a>');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`post_id`, `post_url`, `post_title`, `post_image`, `post_excerpt`, `blog_id`, `post_timestamp`, `post_content`) VALUES
(970, 'http://blogbaladi.com/lebanese-ministry-of-energy-and-water-new-ad-campaign/', 'Lebanese Ministry of Energy And Water New Ad Campaign', 'http://blogbaladi.com/images/20130405_074525-425x273.jpg', 'A friend was telling me that she spotted new ads for the Lebanese Ministry of Energy and Water yesterday, one showing a ...', 'blogbaladi', 1365142500, '<p><img src="http://blogbaladi.com/images/20130405_074525-425x273.jpg" alt="20130405_074525" width="425" height="273"></p>\n<p>A friend was telling me that she spotted new ads for the Lebanese Ministry of Energy and Water yesterday, one showing a metro/train in the background and another ad showing Lebanese Army men with slogans saying:</p>\n<p>بلدنا صار عندو نفط لتطوير شبكة المواصلات<br>\nOr in English “Now that we have oil, we can enhance the transportation network”<br>\nبلدنا صار عندو نفط لتسليح ودعم الجيش<br>\nor In English “Now that we have oil, we can arm and support the army”</p>\n<p>To begin with, it is still very early to talk about gaining any profits from the exploration of oil and gas as we are still in the per-qualifying round and the first exploration and production agreements are <a href="http://blogbaladi.com/energy-natural-resources/">scheduled</a> to be signed in February 2014.</p>\n<p>Second and more importantly, it is not the lack of money that is preventing our government from funding the Lebanese Army and I think we all know that by now. Added to that, I was hoping that we’d be able to live in peace with the neighbors (the ones we acknowledge and the one we don’t) and focus on improving the country and making life better for the Lebanese after these finds and I believe this is what we should put our hopes on (Look at the Qatari Model for example).</p>\n<p>Last but not least, I saw the ad with the train (or Metro) in the background but I couldn’t take a shot of it. I don’t know how feasible this project is and I will be waiting to see if the minister in question has any future plans for that specially with the lack of urban planning or any planning in this country.</p>\n<p>All in all, it’s very nice to dream and let people dream of a wealthy country with a solid infrastructure, prosperous economy and a strong army but at the moment, most Lebanese are dreaming of leaving the country and struggling to have a lira in their pockets at the end of the month. So it wouldn’t hurt if all officials got down to Earth for a second and reached out to the people’s real needs instead of living in lalaland.</p>\n<p><em>Thank you Hala</em></p>'),
(971, 'http://blogbaladi.com/beirut-city-centre-now-open/', 'Beirut City Centre Now Open', 'http://blogbaladi.com/images/564562_10152713596490080_2126216138_n-375x500.jpg', 'Picture taken by Gino\nHere are few pictures of the Beirut City Centre that opened yesterday. There are a lot of shops an...', 'blogbaladi', 1365145260, '<p><img src="http://blogbaladi.com/images/564562_10152713596490080_2126216138_n-375x500.jpg" alt="564562_10152713596490080_2126216138_n" width="375" height="500"><br><em>Picture taken by <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Ginoraidy">Gino</a></em></p>\n<p>Here are few pictures of the Beirut City Centre that opened yesterday. There are a lot of shops and restaurants that are still not open such as the Cheese Cake Factory, Shake Shack and Fat Burger but they are coming very soon from what I heard. Carrefour was the main attraction yesterday as they were offering a lot of items with great discounts.</p>\n<p>I am passing by this weekend so I will have more pictures and information to share.</p>\n<p><img src="http://blogbaladi.com/images/image_2-425x318.jpg" alt="image_2" width="425" height="318"><br><em>Picture taken by <a href="http://www.plus961.com/">Rami</a></em></p>\n<p><img src="http://blogbaladi.com/images/image_4-425x318.jpg" alt="image_4" width="425" height="318"><br><em>Picture taken by <a href="http://www.plus961.com/">Rami</a></em></p>'),
(972, 'http://ritakml.info/2013/04/05/mom-i-cant-log-out/', 'Mom: I can’t log out!', NULL, 'Mom: I can’t log out!\nMe: Chileh el cookies.\nMom: Mech 3emleh gher ma3moul ya mama!\n \nThe post Mom: I can’t log out...', 'ritakml', 1365147420, '<p>Mom: I can’t log out!</p>\n<p>Me: Chileh el cookies.</p>\n<p>Mom: Mech 3emleh gher ma3moul ya mama!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a data-href="http://ritakml.info/2013/04/05/mom-i-cant-log-out/"></a><a data-count="horizontal" data-url="http://ritakml.info/2013/04/05/mom-i-cant-log-out/" data-text="Mom: I can’t log out!"></a><a data-href="http://ritakml.info/2013/04/05/mom-i-cant-log-out/"></a><a href="http://www.addtoany.com/share_save#url=http%3A%2F%2Fritakml.info%2F2013%2F04%2F05%2Fmom-i-cant-log-out%2F&title=Mom%3A%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20log%20out%21"><img src="http://ritakml.info/wp-content/plugins/add-to-any/share_save_120_16.png" width="120" height="16" alt="share save 120 16 Mom: I cant log out!" title="share save 120 16 photo"></a></p><p>The post <a href="http://ritakml.info/2013/04/05/mom-i-cant-log-out/">Mom: I can’t log out!</a> appeared first on <a href="http://ritakml.info/">ritakml.info</a>.</p>'),
(973, 'http://www.plush-beirut.net/2013/04/street-style-beirut-central-district.html', 'Street Style: Beirut Central District', 'http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nX3dROvyiJk/UV6B09e84nI/AAAAAAAABt0/glUPXmFcaQg/s640/IMG_0206.JPG', 'Plush Beirut', 'plush-beirut', 1365148140, '<div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nX3dROvyiJk/UV6B09e84nI/AAAAAAAABt0/glUPXmFcaQg/s1600/IMG_0206.JPG" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="426" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nX3dROvyiJk/UV6B09e84nI/AAAAAAAABt0/glUPXmFcaQg/s640/IMG_0206.JPG" width="640"></a></div><div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QM-_kCxNnd0/UV6B0GckF1I/AAAAAAAABts/GqF7gt2ZFTk/s1600/IMG_0209.JPG" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="426" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QM-_kCxNnd0/UV6B0GckF1I/AAAAAAAABts/GqF7gt2ZFTk/s640/IMG_0209.JPG" width="640"></a></div><div><br></div><br><div>Plush Beirut </div>'),
(974, 'http://ritakml.info/2013/04/05/im-having-trust-issues-%D9%85%D8%B9%D8%B1%D9%83%D8%B4/', 'I’m having trust issues – معركش', 'http://ritakml.info/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/wpid-20130405_094138-1.jpg', 'I love the diversity of names we have; some give a whole different dimension to business.\nThis one one is giving me trus...', 'ritakml', 1365150900, '<p>I love the diversity of names we have; some give a whole different dimension to business.</p>\n<p>This one one is giving me trust issues… :p</p>\n<p>What do you think about the power of names in general?</p>\n<p><a href="http://ritakml.info/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/wpid-20130405_094138-1.jpg"><img title="m3arkach" alt="wpid 20130405 094138 1 Im having trust issues   معركش" src="http://ritakml.info/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/wpid-20130405_094138-1.jpg" width="423" height="421"></a></p>\n<p><a data-href="http://ritakml.info/2013/04/05/im-having-trust-issues-%d9%85%d8%b9%d8%b1%d9%83%d8%b4/"></a><a data-count="horizontal" data-url="http://ritakml.info/2013/04/05/im-having-trust-issues-%d9%85%d8%b9%d8%b1%d9%83%d8%b4/" data-text="I’m having trust issues – معركش"></a><a data-href="http://ritakml.info/2013/04/05/im-having-trust-issues-%d9%85%d8%b9%d8%b1%d9%83%d8%b4/"></a><a href="http://www.addtoany.com/share_save#url=http%3A%2F%2Fritakml.info%2F2013%2F04%2F05%2Fim-having-trust-issues-%25d9%2585%25d8%25b9%25d8%25b1%25d9%2583%25d8%25b4%2F&title=I%E2%80%99m%20having%20trust%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20%D9%85%D8%B9%D8%B1%D9%83%D8%B4"><img src="http://ritakml.info/wp-content/plugins/add-to-any/share_save_120_16.png" width="120" height="16" alt="share save 120 16 Im having trust issues   معركش" title="share save 120 16 photo"></a></p><p>The post <a href="http://ritakml.info/2013/04/05/im-having-trust-issues-%D9%85%D8%B9%D8%B1%D9%83%D8%B4/">I’m having trust issues – معركش</a> appeared first on <a href="http://ritakml.info/">ritakml.info</a>.</p>'),
(975, 'http://seenbymaya.blogspot.com/2013/04/pages-from-rjmag-10-published-next-week.html', '> Pages from RJmag 10, published next week', 'http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-naCcMRFAZcE/UV6PtlEV87I/AAAAAAAABvA/47WfwvVOeoM/s640/01.jpg', 'This season we decided to stay home for summer and shoot right here in our beautiful neighborhood, Mar Mkhayel. Did you ...', 'seenbymaya', 1365152040, 'This season we decided to stay home for summer and shoot right here in our beautiful neighborhood, Mar Mkhayel. Did you know it''s one of the prettiest corners of Beirut?<br>We started at the charming <a href="http://villaclara.fr/villa_clara/page_de_garde.html">Villa Clara</a> hotel, then we moved to <a href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/Frosty-Palace">Frosty Palace</a>, and after that, off to the magnificent stairs by <a href="http://www.facebook.com/Dihzahyners">Paint Up</a>!<br><br><div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-naCcMRFAZcE/UV6PtlEV87I/AAAAAAAABvA/47WfwvVOeoM/s1600/01.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="640" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-naCcMRFAZcE/UV6PtlEV87I/AAAAAAAABvA/47WfwvVOeoM/s640/01.jpg" width="454"></a></div><br><div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-w8CB8R3ipdI/UV6PruGIenI/AAAAAAAABuw/Y5ELDQoxCB4/s1600/02.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="446" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-w8CB8R3ipdI/UV6PruGIenI/AAAAAAAABuw/Y5ELDQoxCB4/s640/02.jpg" width="640"></a></div><br><div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-e1St50JwqAQ/UV6Psunkr-I/AAAAAAAABu4/gqdXamJGkjk/s1600/03.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="444" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-e1St50JwqAQ/UV6Psunkr-I/AAAAAAAABu4/gqdXamJGkjk/s640/03.jpg" width="640"></a></div><br><div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-eoWLW5KsmVo/UV6PwNri2wI/AAAAAAAABvI/Yof94Ki1b4U/s1600/05.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="446" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-eoWLW5KsmVo/UV6PwNri2wI/AAAAAAAABvI/Yof94Ki1b4U/s640/05.jpg" width="640"></a></div><br><div><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-AwnxtF_JMuU/UV6Px9U40vI/AAAAAAAABvQ/ZjAgJQZgfHw/s1600/04.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="448" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-AwnxtF_JMuU/UV6Px9U40vI/AAAAAAAABvQ/ZjAgJQZgfHw/s640/04.jpg" width="640"></a></div><br>The second say we shot the swimwear at the sandy beach of Okaibeh, with a section about all the hand signs in Beach Volleyball...<br><div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-iNvh6Jh9AyQ/UV6Qb9py4tI/AAAAAAAABvY/LySnmOvmNHA/s1600/06.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="444" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-iNvh6Jh9AyQ/UV6Qb9py4tI/AAAAAAAABvY/LySnmOvmNHA/s640/06.jpg" width="640"></a></div><br><div><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-7O4jDogczog/UV6Qct3xFiI/AAAAAAAABvg/ajCVfGPXlEY/s1600/08.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="446" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-7O4jDogczog/UV6Qct3xFiI/AAAAAAAABvg/ajCVfGPXlEY/s640/08.jpg" width="640"></a></div><br><div><a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QGmupbXmvjU/UV6QclxCu6I/AAAAAAAABvk/1BKZLltl_P0/s1600/07.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="446" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QGmupbXmvjU/UV6QclxCu6I/AAAAAAAABvk/1BKZLltl_P0/s640/07.jpg" width="640"></a></div><br><div><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Lz4mv1FRCOo/UV6QdZnl3kI/AAAAAAAABvw/6_5jhGhMqDA/s1600/09.jpg" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="640" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Lz4mv1FRCOo/UV6QdZnl3kI/AAAAAAAABvw/6_5jhGhMqDA/s640/09.jpg" width="454"></a></div><br><br>And if you feel like a sneak peek at the making of, here you go:<br><br><iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/-xDIpLXuFyI" width="560"></iframe>'),
(976, 'http://ginosblog.com/2013/04/05/city-center-is-now-open-photos-and-updated-list-of-new-brands/', 'Beirut City Centre is Now Open – Photos and Updated List of New Brands', NULL, 'I went down with my dearest sister yesterday to check out the brand new and almost fully-open Beirut City Centre. We wer...', 'ginosblog', 1365152460, '<p>I went down with my dearest sister yesterday to check out the brand new and almost fully-open Beirut City Centre. We were not disappointed and spent almost the whole day there browsing the shops (many of which are new) and then having lunch at the food court. I was bummed out that the rooftop wasn’t open yet (where Cheesecake Factory and Shake Shack are located) and that Fatburger needed till Saturday to become fully operational. Otherwise though, no mentionable hiccups.</p>\n<p>The crowds at Carrefour were insane. <em>E</em><em>veryone</em> had an LED TV in their shopping carts because they were selling for pretty cheap: 300-330USD a piece, and Samsung smart TVs for 750USD or so. Apart from Carrefour, there are over 40 brands that are new to Lebanon, which is almost 1 out of 4 stores in the mall. Some of the brand new stores are:</p>\n<ol><li><span>Victoria’s Secret</span></li>\n<li>Carrefour</li>\n<li>Cheesecake Factory</li>\n<li>Shake Shack</li>\n<li>Fatburger</li>\n<li>G-Star Raw</li>\n<li>Jack Wills</li>\n<li>Warehouse</li>\n<li>Wallis</li>\n<li>Dorothy Perkins</li>\n<li>Pottery Barn Kids</li>\n<li>West Elm</li>\n<li>Payless Shoe Source</li>\n<li>Marks and Spencer</li>\n<li>Magic Planet</li>\n<li>Atilla</li>\n<li>Express</li>\n<li>VOX Cinemas</li>\n</ol><a href="http://ginosblog.com/2013/04/05/city-center-is-now-open-photos-and-updated-list-of-new-brands/20130404_151042/" title="20130404_151042"><img data-liked="0" data-reblogged="0" data-attachment-id="12895" data-orig-file="http://ginoraidy.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130404_151042.jpg" data-orig-size="2448,3264" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta=''{"aperture":"2.6",