te flower"><img data-liked="0" data-reblogged="0" data-attachment-id="5605" data-orig-file="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_150829.jpg" data-orig-size="612,816" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta=''{"aperture":"2.6","credit":"","camera":"GT-N7100","caption":"","created_timestamp":"1365520109","copyright":"","focal_length":"3.7","iso":"80","shutter_speed":"0.00078864353312303","title":""}'' data-image-title="white flower" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_150829.jpg?w=225" data-large-file="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_150829.jpg?w=560" width="112" height="150" src="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_150829.jpg?w=112&h=150" alt="white flower"></a>\n<a href="http://smileyface80.wordpress.com/2013/04/10/%D9%88%D9%82%D9%85%D8%AD/20130409_150948_1/" title="special white flower"><img data-liked="0" data-reblogged="0" data-attachment-id="5607" data-orig-file="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_150948_1.jpg" data-orig-size="429,572" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta=''{"aperture":"2.6","credit":"","camera":"GT-N7100","caption":"","created_timestamp":"1365520188","copyright":"","focal_length":"3.7","iso":"80","shutter_speed":"0.0016129032258065","title":""}'' data-image-title="special white flower" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_150948_1.jpg?w=225" data-large-file="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_150948_1.jpg?w=429" width="112" height="150" src="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_150948_1.jpg?w=112&h=150" alt="special white flower"></a>\n<a href="http://smileyface80.wordpress.com/2013/04/10/%D9%88%D9%82%D9%85%D8%AD/20130409_151001/" title="white and pink"><img data-liked="0" data-reblogged="0" data-attachment-id="5608" data-orig-file="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_151001.jpg" data-orig-size="612,816" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta=''{"aperture":"2.6","credit":"","camera":"GT-N7100","caption":"","created_timestamp":"1365520201","copyright":"","focal_length":"3.7","iso":"80","shutter_speed":"0.00065104166666667","title":""}'' data-image-title="white and pink" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_151001.jpg?w=225" data-large-file="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_151001.jpg?w=560" width="112" height="150" src="http://smileyface80.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/20130409_151001.jpg?w=112&h=150" alt="white and pink"></a>\n\n<p>For more photos, please visit my <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/smileyface80/" target="_blank">flickr page</a>, and you can now follow me on <a href="http://instagram.com/smileyface_80#" target="_blank">instagram</a></p>\n<p>للمزيد من الصور يمكنكم زيارة صفحتي على <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/smileyface80/" target="_blank">فليكر</a>, والانضمام الى صفحتي على <a href="http://instagram.com/smileyface_80#" target="_blank">انستغرام</a></p>\n<br>Filed under: <a href="http://smileyface80.wordpress.com/category/bisan-photostream/">Bisan Photostream</a>  <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/smileyface80.wordpress.com/5598/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/smileyface80.wordpress.com/5598/"></a> <img alt="" border="0" src="http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=smileyface80.wordpress.com&blog=9248528&post=5598&subd=smileyface80&ref=&feed=1" width="1" height="1">'),
(1123, 'http://ivysays.com/2013/04/10/wtf-of-the-day/', 'WTF of the Day', 'http://ivysays.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/img_4176.jpg?w=500&h=375', 'Damn you Photoshop.\nNo Auto Khaled did not commission Nigella Lawson for their latest campaign. At least I hope they did...', 'ivysays', 1365574200, '<p><a href="http://ivysays.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/img_4176.jpg"><img alt="IMG_4176" src="http://ivysays.files.wordpress.com/2013/04/img_4176.jpg?w=500&h=375" width="500" height="375"></a></p>\n<p>Damn you Photoshop.</p>\n<p>No Auto Khaled did not commission <strong><a href="http://www.nigella.com/">Nigella Lawson </a></strong>for their latest campaign. At least I hope they didn’t.</p>\n<p>Some bright graphic designer thought it would be a brilliant idea to paste her photo in there and call it a day. I’m really curious as to how that process went down, are they even aware who <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nigella_Lawson">Nigella</a> is or were they just randomly googling an image say “women holding bag of crisps” and found Nigella handling some buttered cream puff or about to stuff her face with something ridiculously roasted lamb shack and so he intricately replaced it with a truck like it’s the most natural thing in the world?</p>\n<p>Lebanese brilliance at it’s finest hour. Brands take note of this. I want to nominate them for an <a href="http://www.smabeirut.com/">SMA</a>.</p>\n<p>Speaking of<a href="http://www.smabeirut.com/"> SMA</a> did you vote for me? Best Fashion Blog, it’ll only take a sec here you go <a href="http://www.smabeirut.com/" rel="nofollow">http://www.smabeirut.com/</a></p>\n<br><a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/ivysays.wordpress.com/5347/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/ivysays.wordpress.com/5347/"></a> <img alt="" border="0" src="http://stats.wordpress.com/b.gif?host=ivysays.com&blog=11241585&post=5347&subd=ivysays&ref=&feed=1" width="1" height="1">'),
